{"tid":769902,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[勵志]的士陳:2018年8月,而我不知 W 是誰","createTime":"2018-08-06T14:27:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-06T14:27:33.000Z","uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"0017d4a0c0dfa95b4e5f7fa48d64f0fd1c526345","tid":769902,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T14:27:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180806/58531302\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180806%2F58531302&d=xdIU%2BrzGFHX3CxxFNyih5EbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=0d8c1268\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180806%2F58531302&h=689fbecf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180806/58531302</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n當日比黃x 明咁串,敗走強國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今日天然人 Y 同海綿蛋糕仲唔收皮 ?!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n台灣ETtoday星光雲引述消息人士指出，被指涉及陰陽合同的內地女星范冰冰，早前被警方逮補後獲釋，限制出境，但今日（6日）再度被捕。報道稱，內部人員全數噤聲，網上同時傳出，當局接下來要調查的對象還有Y姓女星，以及W姓男偶像。<br />\n<br />\n報道引述消息人士指出，范冰冰在上月29日被要求到案說明，經過2天後獲釋，但未透露今日再次被捕的詳情。<br />\n報道又稱，網上瘋傳下一個被調查的對象是「<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Y</span>姓女星」，她擁有自己的工作室，出資拍攝戲劇作品，並有多位旗下藝人參與演出。由於她和另一位<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">W</span>姓男偶像手上代言無數，如果也因為稅務問題接受調查，表演事業也會連帶受到影響。"}]}